Package au.gov.naa.digipres.xena.kernel.properties

Class Summary
PluginProperties Abstract class representing the set of properties for a plugin.
PropertiesDialog Xena poperty dialog
A dialog which will display a method for modifying the property value for each XenaProperty in the given list (for example a simple text entry field for String properties, a text entry field and a Browse button for File properties, etc).
PropertiesManager LoadManager for properties.
PropertiesMenuListener Listener class to listen for selections in a Properties Menu, and display the properties dialog for the selected plugin.
PropertyValuePanel A panel containing specific component(s) to change the value of this property.
XenaProperty Class representing a property of a plugin.
 

Enum Summary
XenaProperty.PropertyType  
 

Exception Summary
InvalidPropertyException Exception class to indicate that an attempt has been made to set an invalid property.
PropertyMessageException Indicates that an operation on a plugin property has triggered a message which should be displayed, logged etc by the calling application.
